eatures/glastonbury-2025-headliners-rumours-3773153">谁将成为明年的三个头条</a>新闻。</p><p> Alanis Morissette邮报宣布，在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alanis-morissette-announces-huge-london-summer-2025-show-at-o2-with-liz-phair-3843143">Liz Phair在O2举行的伦敦2025年大型演出</a>。</p> ;
 Nia Archives向我们介绍了丛林的复兴，并制作了一张“快乐”的新专辑https://www.nme.com/news/music/nia-archives-brits-interview-jungle-resurgence-resurgence-jamie-jamie-jamie-xx-happier-new-new-album-3843124?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = nia-archives-brits-interview-jungle-resurgence-jamie-jamie-xx-happier-new-albumLiberty Dunworth Mon, 03 Mar 2025 13:18:05 +0000 Music InterviewsMusic NewsNewsBRIT AwardsJungle https://www.nme.com/?p=3843124 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="NIA档案参加2025年英国奖" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我只想制作一张新专辑。我想享受我的生活，去一些假期，玩一些节日并实现梦想”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nia-archives-brits-interview-jungle-resurgence-jamie-xx-happier-new-album-3843124">NIA档案馆向我们介绍了丛林的复兴，并制作了“更快乐”的新专辑，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="NIA档案参加2025年英国奖" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nia-archives">Nia Archives</a>近年来与<em>NME</em>谈到了Jungle的复兴，并透露她正在制作一张“更快乐的”新专辑。阅读下面的采访，或观看上面的视频。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nia-archives-silence-is-loud-review-lyrics-tracklist-3616549">NIA档案 - “沉默是大声”评论：来自必不可少的新星的反射丛林</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手，制片人和DJ本周末在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">2025年英国奖</a>的红地毯上遇到了<em>NME</em> ，并讨论了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drum-n-bass-streams-rocket-by-94-per-cent-in-three-years-says-spotify-3823613">Drum n&#39;Bass和Jungle在过去三年中的流行程度大大增加</a>。</p><p>这是因为<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/spotify">Spotify</a>在2024年底分享了一些统计数据，这证实，自2021年以来，该流派的溪流已增长了94％。NIA被列为最受欢迎的艺术家，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chase-status">Chase＆State</a> ，Bou， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bou">Bou</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rudimental">Rudementiment</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/goddard">Rudimenty，Goddard。</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sub-focus">Sub Focus</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charlotte-plank">Charlotte Plank</a> 。</p><p> NME告诉<em>NME</em> ：“丛林和鼓n&#39;Bass总是存在于地下，历史上总是有交叉曲调，因此看到年轻人开始音乐真是太酷了。” “我认为那些跨界音乐一直在将人们带入这个地下音乐的世界。”</p><p>她还向<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-nia-archives-exhilarating-remix-of-jamie-xxs-waited-all-night-3816148">杰米XX的歌曲“ Waite All Night”的封面</a>点头，将其描述为跨界曲目，她希望在其中创建铁杆和丛林的融合。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="杰米xx-等待整夜。" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8ruwv4PVXf4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Nia解释说：“他问我是否会进行混音，我就像&#39;你知道，我想知道&#39;。” “我喜欢他的音乐，我想和它一起做一些快乐的阵线融合。”最初的曲目在杰米XX的最新专辑《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jamie-xx-in-waves-review-3794408">海浪</a>》中出现，并以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/romy-madley-croft">罗米（Romy）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oliver-sim">奥利弗·西姆（Oliver Sim）</a> （他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-xx">XX</a>的乐队成员）为特色。</p><p> Bradford DJ分享了粉丝可以期待的东西，他分享了她已经在努力进行广受好评的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nia-archives-silence-is-loud-review-lyrics-tracklist-3616549">Silence Is Is Out</a> ”专辑的后续专辑，并希望将她的音乐朝着更加乐观的方向发展。</p><p> “我只想制作一张新专辑。我想享受我的生活，去一些假期，播放一些节日并实现梦想。”她继续说道。 “我已经制作了几首歌，所以我很高兴创建比上次更好的专辑。我比[带有&#39;Silence Is Loud&#39;]更快乐，所以希望这是一张比以前更快乐的专辑。” </p><figure id="attachment_3843128" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3843128" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3843128" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives-brits@2000x1270.jpg" alt="NIA档案参加2025年英国奖" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives-brits@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives-brits@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives-brits@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives-brits@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives-brits@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/nia-archives-brits@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3843128" class="wp-caption-text"> NIA档案参加2025年英国颁奖典礼。荣誉：Jim Dyson/Redferns/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Nia Archives去年发布了她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mercury-prize-2024-tv-and-radio-programme-announced-3785881">水星奖</a>的首张唱片LP，并受到<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nia-archives-silence-is-loud-review-lyrics-tracklist-3616549"><em>NME的发光四星级评论。</em></a>它写道：“她散发着信心，不再将自己的声音隐藏在邪恶的生产技巧之后。”</p><p> “随着每个项目，Nia都会在整个唱片中植入了她所植入的思想和概念的种子。而且，在她的首张专辑中，他们都蓬勃发展为一张丰富而自我反射的唱片，显示了艺术家超越节奏。”</p><p>在英国2025年，尼亚（Nia）与<a href="/artists-charli-xcx">贝基</a><a href="/artists/becky-hill">·希尔（Becky Hill）</a> ，蔡斯（Chase＆Sucation）和<a href="/artists/fred-again">弗雷德（Fred）</a>一起被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">提名为最佳舞蹈表演</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-brit-awards-2025-3842577">在此处</a>找到获奖者的完整列表。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nia-archives-brits-interview-jungle-resurgence-jamie-xx-happier-new-album-3843124">NIA档案馆向我们介绍了丛林的复兴，并制作了“更快乐”的新专辑，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Beabadoobee与Sabrina Carpenter一起表演并拥抱不完美：“我认为那是一个美丽” https://www.nme.com/news/music/beabadoobee-brits-interview-sabrina-carpenter-embracing-imbracing-imperfection-3843092?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = babadoobee-brits-interview-sabrina-carpenter-embracing-imperfectionLiberty Dunworth Mon, 03 Mar 2025 13:12:04 +0000 Music InterviewsMusic NewsNewsBRIT AwardsIndiePophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3843092 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Beabadoobee参加2025年英国奖" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手兼作曲家还向NME介绍了她认为粉丝可以找到她即将举行的节目的“烦人”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beabadoobee-brits-interview-sabrina-carpenter-embracing-imperfection-3843092">Beabadoobee帖子与Sabrina Carpenter一起表演，并拥抱了不完美：“我认为这是一种美丽”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Beabadoobee参加2025年英国奖" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beabadoobee">Beabadoobee</a>与<em>NME</em>谈到了她即将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a>举行的伦敦演出，以及为什么她认为在音乐中拥抱不完美很重要的原因。阅读下面的采访，或观看上面的视频。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beabadoobee-this-is-how-tomorrow-moves-review-3780598">Beabadoobee  - “这就是明天的移动方式”评论：美丽的女性肖像</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手，词曲作者和吉他手在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">黑人2025年的</a>红地毯上与<em>NME</em>相遇。在当晚，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">都参加了年度艺术家和Alt/Rock Act</a> ，尽管该奖项最终获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">Sam Fender</a> 。</p><p> Beabadoobe在接受<em>NME</em>讲话时，就她 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beabadoobee-on-the-importance-of-imperfect-songs-3825425">最近关于在歌曲创作中拥抱瑕疵的评论</a>以及她认为与粉丝诚实很重要的原因公开了。 “我认为错误中有一个美丽。听到某人艺术的原始性对我来说很酷，这就是为什么我最喜欢简单的歌曲。”她说。</p><p>她还详细阐述了自己如何在自己的音乐中捕捉到这一点的方式，并补充说：“我弹吉他，但我没有被音乐家训练。因此，我与之编写的和弦并不是最技术性，最狡猾的和弦进度。</p><p> “这就是我的依赖，试图找到一种使某物栩栩如生的旋律。我认为其中有美。” </p><figure id="attachment_3843101" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3843101" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3843101" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee-brits@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Beabadoobee参加2025年英国奖" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee-brits@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee-brits@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee-brits@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee-brits@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee-brits@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/beabadoobee-brits@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3843101" class="wp-caption-text"> Beabadoobee参加了2025年英国奖。信贷：扮演/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>Beabadoobee还讨论了她今年夏天即将在伦敦举行的演出，在那里她将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-second-show-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-2025-buy-tickets-3839275">在BST Hyde Park的巨大标题表演中加入Sabrina Carpenter</a> 。</p><p> “我很高兴[获得支持插槽]。她是如此可爱，我们已经讲了几次，所以我迫不及待地想这样做。这真的很有趣！我喜欢在现实生活中分享我的音乐。”</p><p>她继续说：“至于我一生的期望，每个人都说我有大约10个吉他更改。实际上，我很害怕人们会为此感到烦恼，因为我不断地改变吉他。但是期望很多不同的颜色吉他！”</p><p>从那里开始，Beabadoobee也将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beabadoobee-announces-the-space-in-between-2025-us-tour-buy-tickets-3834660">前往美国的标题巡回演出</a>。这些节目支持她的第三张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beabadoobee-this-is-how-tomorrow-moves-review-3780598">This Is Tomorrow Moves</a> 》，该专辑 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beabadoobee-this-is-how-tomorrow-moves-review-3780598">由<em>NME</em>进行了四星级评论</a>。</p><p> “ [&#39;Girl Song&#39;]是一首令人痛苦的歌曲，充满了许多复杂且经常矛盾的情绪，年轻女性的棘手现实是裸露的。” “这就是整个&#39;这就是明天的移动&#39;的闪耀 -  Beabadoobee的诀窍，可以捕捉与坦率相关的坦率的曲折。这位年轻艺术家的第三张唱片是一系列展示了这次纠结感的歌曲，这是一件凄美，有力的事情。” </p><figure id="attachment_3843104" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3843104" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3843104" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sabrina-Carpenter@2000x1270.jpg" alt="萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）在2025年英国颁奖典礼上演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sabrina-Carpenter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sabrina-Carpenter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sabrina-Carpenter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sabrina-Carpenter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sabrina-Carpenter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sabrina-Carpenter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3843104" class="wp-caption-text">萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）在2025年英国颁奖典礼上表演。</figcaption></figure><p>在2025年的英国奖项上，萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sabrina-carpenters-eye-catching-medley-from-the-brit-awards-2025-3842606">以她最大的曲目大为打开了演出</a>。这位流行歌星还获得了年度国际艺术家和年度国际歌曲类别的提名，尽管两个奖杯最终都去了前<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/chappell-roan-05-02-2024-3582467"><em>NME</em>封面明星</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）</a> 。</p><p>您可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-brit-awards-2025-3842577">在此处</a>找到Brits 2025获奖者的完整列表，并<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fbeabadoobee-tickets%2Fartist%2F2618990" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处访问</a>Beabadoobee Tour Dates的剩余门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beabadoobee-brits-interview-sabrina-carpenter-embracing-imperfection-3843092">Beabadoobee帖子与Sabrina Carpenter一起表演，并拥抱了不完美：“我认为这是一种美丽”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
